text: Chung Sye-kyun (; born 5 November 1950) is a South Korean politician. He was the 42nd Prime Minister of South Korea from January 2020 until April 2021. From 2016 to 2018, he was Speaker of the National Assembly of South Korea. ==References== Category:1950 births Category:Living people Category:Prime Ministers of South Korea Category:Speakers of the National Assembly (South Korea)
title: Chung Sye-kyun
